Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=10}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 5,0:00:10.23,0:00:11.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Everyone, be on your guard! - OG}Em guarda, todos!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:11.53,0:00:13.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:13.62,0:00:17.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If we allow those pirates to infiltrate with so many of us on guard, and it'll be an embarrassment to Galley-La! - OG}{\q2}Se esses piratas entrarem com tantos de nós de guarda,\Nserá uma vergonha pra Galley-La!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:17.80,0:00:19.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não os deixem entrar!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:19.29,0:00:21.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E a porta dos fundos?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:21.05,0:00:24.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Porta dos fundos? Estamos cercando\No prédio inteiro!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:24.61,0:00:25.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There's no blind spot! - OG}{We got no blind spots! - JT}Não tem ponto cego!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:25.88,0:00:29.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Bring it on! We'll take care of all\Nthe Straw Hat Pirates! - OG}Podem vir!\NVamos dar conta de toda a tripulação!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:29.80,0:00:30.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:34.23,0:00:36.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They're all carrying weapons,\Nand they look strong. - OG}Estão todos armados e parecem fortes.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:36.14,0:00:41.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No surprise there. The shipwrights\Nhere beat even pirates. - OG}Sem surpresa. Os carpinteiros\Ndaqui até piratas vencem.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:42.39,0:00:45.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Devíamos ter cuidado\Ne agir na hora certa.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:45.49,0:00:50.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, if we carelessly plunge in,\Nwe'll be in big trouble. - OG}{Yeah, if we mess this up,\Nwe'll be in big trouble. - JT}É, se entrarmos às cegas,\Nvai ficar bem feio pra gente.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:53.43,0:00:56.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Look who's talking! - OG}Olha quem fala!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:56.45,0:01:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He jumped in without any plan this afternoon. - OG}Você mesmo invadiu lá de tarde sem plano nenhum.{JT/Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:01:00.00,0:01:05.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chopper, não sabemos o que vai acontecer.\NNão perca nem o menor movimento.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:05.57,0:01:06.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. - OG}Tá.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:01:07.66,0:01:09.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you see any movement,\Nlet us know immediately. - OG}Avisa a gente na hora se alguém se mexer.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:01:09.83,0:01:11.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim. Entendido.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:11.70,0:01:14.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vai ser uma noite longa,\Nmas não baixem a guarda.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:14.60,0:01:19.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If we miss our chance tonight, we'll have to say goodbye without knowing what happened. - OG}Se perdermos nossa chance essa noite,\Nteremos que partir sem saber o que aconteceu.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:01:20.51,0:01:23.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Think that we won't have a way to go after Robin anymore. - OG}Presumam que essa é\Nnossa última chance de ir atrás da Robin.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:01:24.02,0:01:26.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is where we find out what we're made of. - OG}Agora é a hora de mostrar do que somos feitos.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:01:26.65,0:01:31.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah... We'll definitely capture Robin. - OG}É, vamos trazer a Robin de volta custe o que custar.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.97,0:03:32.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kalifa...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.10,0:03:35.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yes, Iceburg-[/i1]san[/i0]. - OG}Sim, Iceburg.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:35.31,0:03:38.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desculpe, mas poderia\Nsair um momento?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:39.16,0:03:40.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Okay. - OG}Sim, senhor.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:40.50,0:03:42.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E mais...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:42.59,0:03:45.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,por favor, mande o Paulie aqui.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:50.24,0:03:51.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Paulie...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:51.11,0:03:52.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:52.13,0:03:54.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Iceburg-[/i1]san[/i0]has something important to tell you. - OG}O Iceburg tem\Nalgo importante pra te dizer.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.40,0:03:56.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{With me? - OG}Comigo?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:56.65,0:03:58.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim, só com você.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:58.43,0:04:02.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estarei no meu escritório.\NÉ só me chamar se algo acontecer.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:03.85,0:04:04.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.24,0:04:09.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Taking the trouble to have a talk alone\Nat a time like this... - OG}De todas as horas pra ter uma conversa particular...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.76,0:04:11.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que diabos será que é?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:11.61,0:04:12.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sei lá.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:13.30,0:04:14.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A will? - OG}Últimas palavras?!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:17.08,0:04:20.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela disse que era importante.\NEntra lá e fala com ele logo.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:20.55,0:04:22.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-É...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:22.81,0:04:25.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shall we stay a little\Nways away from the door? - OG}Vamos nos afastar um pouco da porta?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:25.70,0:04:27.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. - OG}É melhor.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:32.30,0:04:35.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que será que ele precisa\Nfalar com o Paulie?!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.60,0:04:39.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's Iceburg-[/i1]san[/i0]we're talking about.\NIt must be very important. - OG}Estamos falando do Iceburg.\NDeve ser muito importante.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:39.41,0:04:42.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{More importantly,\Nour current problem is those pirates. - OG}Mais importante, temos que\Nlidar com esses piratas.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.20,0:04:43.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.50,0:04:47.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De acordo com a investigação da Kalifa,\Nsão sete.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:47.99,0:04:52.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O capitão, Chapéu de Palha Luffy.\NCaçador de Piratas Zoro e Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:52.70,0:04:57.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Tem também a garota que foi na Doca Um\Nhoje de tarde e o rapaz com o nariz comprido e arredondado.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:58.25,0:05:03.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. There're two others besides those. That's everyone. Coo coo! - OG}{Yeah. There were two others, and that was it. - JT}É. Além dos mencionados,\Ntêm mais dois, e é isso.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:03.60,0:05:06.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Their purpose is the least of our problems. - OG}O objetivo deles não nos interessa.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:06.24,0:05:09.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entrar aqui será\Na última coisa que farão.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:10.10,0:05:14.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We'll bring them all down together. Coo coo! - OG}Vamos acabar com a tripulação inteira\Nde uma vez por todas.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:14.46,0:05:16.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:18.57,0:05:21.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo... Entendido.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:21.76,0:05:25.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso pode ser muito arriscado.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:25.29,0:05:28.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I thought about it hard,\Nbut you're the only one I can ask this. - OG}Pensei muito nisso,\Nmas você é o único em quem posso confiar.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:29.19,0:05:30.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você faria isso por mim?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.10,0:05:34.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Está me tratando como um estranho.\NPode deixar comigo.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.98,0:05:38.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You have my gratitude. - OG}Obrigado.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:39.62,0:05:41.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, então vou cuidar disso imediatamente.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:41.89,0:05:42.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. - OG}Por favor.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:48.97,0:05:50.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Coo coo... Are you guys done talking? - OG}Terminaram de conversar?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:50.89,0:05:53.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É... Surgiu um imprevisto.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.42,0:05:57.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Sorry, but I have to leave for a bit. Is it okay? - OG}Desculpa, mas preciso sair um pouco, tudo bem?{JT/Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.51,0:06:01.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's fine. The four of us\Nwill be more than enough. - OG}Sem problema. Nós quatro\Nsomos mais que suficiente.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.61,0:06:03.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendo.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:04.10,0:06:06.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Watch over Iceburg-[/i1]san[/i0]. - OG}Cuidem do Iceburg.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:16.91,0:06:18.57,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Escute, Paulie...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.00,0:06:21.53,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Right underneath the desk\Nin the president's office... - OG}Bem debaixo da mesa no meu escritório...{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:21.53,0:06:24.20,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,levante o carpete e encontrará...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.81,0:06:26.61,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,um cofre enterrado ali.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:27.31,0:06:28.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deve ser isso.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:31.62,0:06:34.91,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou te dar a combinação,\Nentão escute com atenção.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.91,0:06:37.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{First, turn it right to 6... - OG}Primeiro, direita... seis...{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:45.09,0:06:45.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Click.}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.69,0:06:48.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vocês estão prontos?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:48.51,0:06:50.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, estamos prontos.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.60,0:06:53.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Então vou causar uma distração.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:53.00,0:06:57.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The other four of you, please carry out\Nyour own mission after the signal. - OG}Os quatro vão executar\Nsuas missões após o sinal.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.40,0:06:58.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendido.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:59.87,0:07:01.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pronta, Nico Robin?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim... a qualquer momento.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:12.22,0:07:13.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uma explosão!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.25,0:07:19.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What was that explosion?! - OG}O que foi essa explosão agora?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:19.59,0:07:20.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tragam água, agora!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.85,0:07:23.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Levem os feridos pra um lugar seguro!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:23.05,0:07:25.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rápido! Apaguem o fogo!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:25.59,0:07:28.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,F-Foi tiro de canhão?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:28.01,0:07:30.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não, não veio de fora!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:30.90,0:07:32.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It was set up to explode! - OG}{Someone set it to explode! - JT}Alguém deve ter armado!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:32.55,0:07:34.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Apaguem o fogo!\NRápido, apaguem o fogo!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:34.99,0:07:37.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Someone! Give me a hand! - OG}Alguém, me dá uma mão!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What a showy signal... - OG}Que sinal chamativo...{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:42.46,0:07:43.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:49.23,0:07:51.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The explosion happened\Nin the north corner of the first floor! - OG}A explosão foi no canto\Nnorte do primeiro andar.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:51.71,0:07:52.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todo mundo está bem?!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.85,0:07:57.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{At least half of you stay at your post!\NWe still haven't seen the enemy! - OG}Metade de vocês fiquem no posto!\NAinda não vimos o inimigo!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:57.68,0:08:00.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{To prepare for an attack,\Nstrengthen the defenses! - OG}Reforcem o perímetro\Ne preparem-se para um ataque!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.35,0:08:03.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't let them come in the building! - OG}Não os deixem entrar no prédio!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.12,0:08:08.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you okay, Iceburg-[/i1]san[/i0]?! - OG}Você está bem, Iceburg?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.24,0:08:10.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É... Me assustou.{OG}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:10.73,0:08:12.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vi alguém nas sombras!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:12.69,0:08:14.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's wearing a costume! Catch him! - OG}Está usando uma fantasia! Peguem ela!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lá vêm eles!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:17.41,0:08:18.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deixa comigo!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:19.40,0:08:20.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll nail them! - OG}Vou pegar eles!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:20.40,0:08:21.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Wait! - OG}Ei, espera!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:22.90,0:08:24.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Geez... - OG}Meu Deus...{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:29.82,0:08:32.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por aqui! Peguem ela!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:32.10,0:08:33.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não deixem ela escapar!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:33.41,0:08:36.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's just by himself! Corner him! - OG}Está sozinha! Encurrala ela!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.33,0:08:38.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Come on! Assassin pirate! - OG}Vem, pirata assassina!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:55.80,0:08:57.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He climbed to a higher floor using a whip! - OG}Subiu usando um chicote!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:04.57,0:09:07.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Achou que não teria ninguém no telhado?{OG}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:08.32,0:09:11.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não subestime os carpinteiros da Galley-La.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:11.50,0:09:14.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como ousam nos zombar\Ntentando um assassinato?!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:14.66,0:09:17.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Prepare-se, pirata!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:17.50,0:09:20.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nós definitivamente não vamos\Nperdoar vocês!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:21.55,0:09:25.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You'd better not try anything. You're no match for me. - OG}Não tente nada. Você não é páreo pra mim.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:27.75,0:09:29.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tem dois aqui!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estão indo pra porta dos fundos!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:33.57,0:09:37.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't let them get away! We'll attack from both sides! Don't let them inside! - OG}Não os percam! Ataquem dos dois lados!\NNão os deixem entrar!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Follow them! Capture them immediately! - OG}{Move! Take them down now! - JT}Mexam-se! Capturem eles imediatamente!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:45.50,0:09:49.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You have the blueprints of his residence\Nin your head, right? - OG}{You memorized his residence's layout, right, Nico Robin? - JT}Você memorizou a planta\Nda residência dele, certo, Nico Robin?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.15,0:09:50.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:54.02,0:09:56.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ahh... Os carpinteiros estão em polvorosa.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:56.87,0:10:00.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. It's gotten quite noisy. - OG}{Yeah. It's gettin' pretty rowdy. - JT}É... Tá bem barulhento lá embaixo.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:02.91,0:10:06.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What do we do? Shall we go in soon? - OG}O que fazemos?\NDevíamos entrar logo.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:07.92,0:10:09.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm? Onde está o Luffy?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:09.38,0:10:11.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Quêeee?!\N– Quêeee?!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:12.14,0:10:16.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Think thoroughly before you take action! - OG}– Pensa antes de agir!\N– Pensa antes de agir!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:16.72,0:10:20.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You dumbass captain! - OG}– Capitão idiota!\N– Capitão idiota!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:21.52,0:10:22.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you just realizing that? - OG}Tarde demais pra isso...{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:23.51,0:10:26.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A porta dos fundos! Estão indo pra\Nporta dos fundos! Encurrala eles!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:26.50,0:10:28.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não deixem escapar! Cerquem eles!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:34.97,0:10:39.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How dare you show your faces\Nin front of all us guards?! - OG}Vocês querem morrer, aparecendo\Nna frente de todos esses guardas?!{JT/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:39.54,0:10:42.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't make light of the craftsmen at Galley-La! - OG}Não subestimem os carpinteiros da Galley-La!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:42.07,0:10:46.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Your fate was already decided\Nwhen you hurt Iceburg-san! - OG}O destino de vocês foi selado quando\Ncolocaram a mão no Iceburg!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.75,0:10:47.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desistam!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.50,0:10:53.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You can no longer escape, pirates! - OG}Vocês não vão a lugar nenhum, piratas!{JT/Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.15,0:10:55.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desistam e mostrem suas caras!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:55.41,0:11:00.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We're gonna drag out the rest\Nof the group using you two! Damn assassins! - OG}Vocês dois vão ser isca pro\Nresto da tripulação, malditos assassinos!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:09.84,0:11:11.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele vai fazer alguma coisa!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:11.19,0:11:13.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Atirem!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:31.51,0:11:33.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles desapareceram... Impossível!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:33.64,0:11:34.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:34.96,0:11:37.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pra onde foram?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.65,0:11:46.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, você está bem?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:47.54,0:11:51.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela é forte... O que é aquela do chicote?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:51.40,0:11:53.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{She ran... in the air. - OG}Ela correu... pelo ar.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:54.41,0:11:55.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Impossível...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:56.22,0:11:58.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ran in the air? - OG}Correu pelo ar...?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:59.60,0:12:03.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sério, vocês nunca escutam, né?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:07.05,0:12:08.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela pulou!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:09.14,0:12:10.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Moon Walk!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:13.51,0:12:16.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's doing it again!\NHe jumped, in the empty air! - OG}Lá vai ela de novo!\NEla pulou no ar!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:19.18,0:12:20.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{Thorny Road! - OG}Briar Road!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:30.08,0:12:33.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I told you not to, didn't I? - OG}Eu disse pra não fazer isso.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:33.92,0:12:35.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ela está vindo!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:35.43,0:12:38.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The courtyard! Go circle around behind her! - OG}Caiu no pátio!\NCirculem por trás dela!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:38.71,0:12:41.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! He went that way! Go ahead of him\Nand hem him in from both sides! - OG}Ei! Por ali!\NCerquem ela dos dois lados!{Z/JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:41.43,0:12:42.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:46.06,0:12:47.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deve ser isso.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:48.64,0:12:49.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I see... - OG}Uau...{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:50.58,0:12:54.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So that's the thing Mr. Iceburg's been hiding, huh? - OG}Então é isso que o Iceburg estava escondendo, né?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.46,0:12:57.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Give it to us. - OG}Passe pra cá.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:00.47,0:13:03.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você não sabe o valor disso.{OG}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:06.34,0:13:08.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem diabos são vocês?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:08.31,0:13:10.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De onde vieram?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:11.28,0:13:12.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The darkness. - OG}Da escuridão.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.62,0:13:17.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{However, we're a group\Nthat carries out justice. - OG}Porém, nosso grupo administra a justiça.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:17.51,0:13:21.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We are Cipher Pol No. 9,\Nan undercover intelligence agency. - OG}Somos a Cipher Pol No. 9,\Numa agência secreta de inteligência.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:23.50,0:13:29.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No matter where you slipped in from, you must've encountered our craftsmen without fail. - OG}De onde quer que tenham vindo,\Ndevem ter encontrado nossos carpinteiros.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:29.10,0:13:30.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Encontramos?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:31.64,0:13:35.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Talvez sim... talvez não...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:36.74,0:13:40.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não me lembro dos detalhes.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:42.07,0:13:46.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is no longer something as simple\Nas an assassination, is it? - OG}Isso não é mais um simples assassinato, certo?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:46.51,0:13:50.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, não lembro de termos chamado assim.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:50.58,0:13:55.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In any case, please give us\Nthat valuable item of Mr. Iceburg's, - OG}De qualquer forma, entregue o objeto\Nvalioso do Iceburg,{JT/Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:55.48,0:13:59.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,e... já que descobriram\Nalgo sobre isso...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:00.57,0:14:03.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{we'd like you to die. - OG}vocês precisam morrer.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:05.26,0:14:07.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Em nome da justiça...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:07.99,0:14:10.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bem aqui... agora mesmo...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:13.03,0:14:15.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Did you find those two who disappeared by the back door?! - OG}Encontraram os dois que\Nsumiram perto da porta dos fundos?!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.06,0:14:18.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não! Não achamos eles em lugar nenhum!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:18.52,0:14:20.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E dentro da residência?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tem guardas em cada janela e porta!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.55,0:14:23.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There's no way they could infiltrate! - OG}Impossível eles entrarem!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:24.24,0:14:27.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Dammit, pirates! Where'd they go?! - OG}Malditos piratas! Pra onde foram?!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:27.12,0:14:29.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They definitely must be hiding nearby! - OG}Devem estar escondidos por perto!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:29.15,0:14:32.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Look carefully one more time!\NCapture them for sure! Got that?! - OG}Continuem procurando! Capturem eles\Ncuste o que custar! Entenderam?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.05,0:14:39.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele está atrás dessa parede.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:41.61,0:14:44.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo. Agora, me empurre.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:51.84,0:14:53.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm shocked. - OG}Você me assustou.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:53.71,0:14:55.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sabia que você viria mais cedo ou mais tarde...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:56.79,0:14:59.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but I never thought\Nyou'd come through there. - OG}mas nunca imaginei que viria por ali...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:59.00,0:15:01.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você fez a mesma coisa ontem à noite?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:01.46,0:15:03.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sei que não tem nenhuma porta ali.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:03.65,0:15:05.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É o poder da Fruta Porta-Porta.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:05.60,0:15:09.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No matter how hard the wall is,\Nthe area I touch becomes a door. - OG}Não importa quão dura seja a parede,\Na área que eu toco se torna uma porta.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:09.93,0:15:13.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{As long as there's a wall,\NI can go in and out anywhere. - OG}Enquanto houver uma parede,\Nposso ir e vir como quiser.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:17.58,0:15:19.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What're you doing?\NWe haven't gotten the signal yet. - OG}O que foi isso?!\NAinda não recebemos o sinal.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:19.85,0:15:23.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You can't call someone weakened\Nwhen he's got enough energy to talk. - OG}Ele não está enfraquecido o bastante\Nse está falando tanto assim.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.25,0:15:28.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Just like a good chef wouldn't neglect\Nto prepare the ingredients beforehand, - OG}Assim como um bom chef não deixaria\Nde preparar os ingredientes antes...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:28.78,0:15:39.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{pros would be careful to restrain their victim so that he wouldn't act unexpectedly before the promised time. - OG}{\q2}profissionais cuidam de imobilizar o alvo para prevenir\Nqualquer ação inesperada antes da hora marcada.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:39.61,0:15:45.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então é assim... que a CP9 faz as coisas, né?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.39,0:15:50.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You've got good insight...\NYou're exactly right. - OG}Você leu bem a situação.\NEstá absolutamente certo.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:54.54,0:15:58.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I did a bad turn to Straw Hat... - OG}Me sinto mal pelo Chapéu de Palha...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:58.61,0:16:01.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So, as I suspected,\Nhe had nothing to do with this. - OG}Parece que ele não tinha nada a ver com isso, afinal.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:03.53,0:16:06.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você não precisa se sentir mal.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.00,0:16:10.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você apenas disse a verdade\Nsobre o que viu ontem à noite.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:14.46,0:16:17.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso também fazia parte do seu plano?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:17.25,0:16:18.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Exato.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.67,0:16:23.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We kept you alive so that\Nthe crime would be pinned on the pirates. - OG}Mantivemos você vivo para colocar\Na culpa nos piratas.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:23.50,0:16:26.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Além disso, se te matássemos de repente...{OG}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.98,0:16:29.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{we wouldn't know the whereabouts of what we're after... - OG}não saberíamos onde encontrar\No que estamos procurando...{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:29.55,0:16:34.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,as plantas de um certo navio.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:34.29,0:16:41.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's something that has been secretly passed down from shipwright to disciple for generations. - OG}É algo que foi secretamente passado\Nde carpinteiro para aprendiz por gerações.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.31,0:16:48.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you felt your life was in danger,\Nyou'd try to entrust it with someone for sure. - OG}Se sentisse que sua vida estava em perigo,\Ncertamente confiaria a alguém...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:49.02,0:16:53.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And the one you chose was Paulie,\None of the foremen at Dock One. - OG}E você escolheu o Paulie,\Num dos capatazes da Doca Um.{Z/JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:54.75,0:16:58.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Our fellow members are with him right now. - OG}Nossos agentes estão com ele agora.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:58.71,0:17:04.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So everything is going... as you planned, huh? - OG}Então tudo está indo...\Nexatamente como planejaram, né?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:05.66,0:17:08.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Make sure things are carried out flawlessly. - OG}Garantam que tudo ocorra perfeitamente até o fim.{JT/Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.92,0:17:08.98,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:09.56,0:17:12.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll go deal with the shipwrights outside the door. - OG}Vou cuidar dos carpinteiros\Ndo outro lado da porta.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:13.54,0:17:18.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Nico Robin, you finish off this man. - OG}Nico Robin, acabe com ele.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:18.60,0:17:22.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quando aqueles dois pegarem as plantas\Ndo Paulie, eles vão te contatar.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:25.36,0:17:28.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Kill Iceburg at that time. - OG}Mate o Iceburg nessa hora.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:29.70,0:17:34.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Nossa missão se completa quando matarmos o Paulie,\Nque descobriu a verdade.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:34.80,0:17:39.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{After that, this crime will be\Npinned entirely on the Straw Hats. - OG}Depois disso, os Chapéus de Palha\Nlevarão toda a culpa.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:44.42,0:17:49.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sério, por que ele não consegue\Nouvir os conselhos dos outros?!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:49.96,0:17:51.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But that's nothing new. - OG}É sempre assim.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:51.75,0:17:56.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas... a Robin pode estar em algum\Nlugar naquela confusão, certo?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.68,0:18:00.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What are we gonna do?!\NWe have to act carefully! - OG}O que vamos fazer?!\NTemos que ter cuidado!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:00.49,0:18:05.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas... dependendo de como\Nvocê olha, tivemos sorte.{OG}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:05.19,0:18:10.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{When Luffy marches into enemy territory, do you think he'd go around to the back or the side?! - OG}Quando o Luffy invade território inimigo,\Nvocê acha que ele vai pela lateral ou por trás?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:10.76,0:18:11.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De jeito nenhum.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:11.75,0:18:13.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nem pensar.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:13.11,0:18:16.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I bet by now he's marched in\Nfrom the front by either jumping in or running, - OG}Aposto que agora ele pulou ou correu\Ndireto pela frente da residência,{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:16.66,0:18:22.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{happy to have found a way in, running around aimlessly with no idea where to go. Sound about right? - OG}feliz por ter entrado e correndo\Npor aí sem rumo. Acertei?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:22.66,0:18:24.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, com certeza.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, sem dúvida.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:25.13,0:18:30.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Right? From the shipwrights' perspective, Luffy is the ringleader of the culprit group. - OG}Certo? Pra os carpinteiros, o Luffy\Né o líder do grupo de criminosos.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:30.70,0:18:34.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Once he jumps in, I bet everyone's attention will go to him! - OG}Quando o protagonista entra em cena,\Ntoda a atenção vai pra ele!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:34.90,0:18:39.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In other words, there's no doubt that the residence's front guard in front of the residence has lightened up for now! - OG}{\q2}Isso quer dizer que podemos supor que\Na guarda da frente está mais leve agora!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:40.38,0:18:45.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So we'll be able to go across that opening and mix in with the crowd\Nof shipwrights who're in an uproar! - OG}Então podemos facilmente atravessar o pátio e nos\Nmisturar na confusão dos carpinteiros!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:45.42,0:18:49.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I see. So thanks to Luffy,\Nthe best chance to infiltrate is right now, huh? - OG}Entendo. Então graças ao Luffy, agora é\Nnossa melhor chance de entrar, né?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:50.57,0:18:53.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's convincing!\NThen, it should be okay to jump in, huh? - OG}Faz sentido! Então dá pra\Nentrar de vez, né?{JT/Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:54.00,0:18:55.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Looks like we can jump over that fence! - OG}Dá pra pular aquela cerca!{Z/JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:55.61,0:18:58.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you guys ready?! - OG}Vamos nessa! Prontos?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:58.47,0:18:59.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Okay, we're gonna go in! - OG}Certo, vamos entrar!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:59.54,0:19:00.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sigam o Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:15.01,0:19:17.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What part of this is light?! - OG}– Como que isso é "mais leve"?!\N– Como que isso é "mais leve"?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:18.57,0:19:21.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga... Não consigo sair.{OG}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:21.64,0:19:25.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,700)}Queria pular pra dentro do prédio\Ntodo descolado...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:26.20,0:19:28.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,475)}mas estou preso e não consigo me mexer!{OG}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:29.90,0:19:32.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}Estou preso e não consigo me mexer...{OG}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:33.05,0:19:34.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,325)}Tenho que me apressar...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:35.35,0:19:39.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera aí, Robin!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:57.89,0:19:59.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que droga está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:01.82,0:20:04.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Alguém! Terceiro andar!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:04.21,0:20:06.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Come to the front\Nof the president's room and the bedroom!}Venham ao corredor do quarto do presidente!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:06.47,0:20:09.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os guardas foram derrubados!\NAlguém! Venham pro andar de cima!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:10.19,0:20:11.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que está dizendo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:12.79,0:20:13.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tilestone{-san}!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:13.71,0:20:16.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Kaku e o Lucci deviam estar lá!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:16.21,0:20:17.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas eles estão...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:17.40,0:20:18.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:29.83,0:20:31.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kaku! Lucci!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:32.34,0:20:36.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Good grief, there's no end to this in sight. No word yet? - OG}Puxa, isso não tem fim.\NAinda sem notícias?{JT/Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:36.72,0:20:38.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seu desgraçado!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:39.61,0:20:42.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como ousa!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:42.84,0:20:44.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que homem barulhento.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:44.77,0:20:48.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Iceburg-[/i1]san[/i0]better be okay! - OG}É melhor o Iceburg estar bem!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:49.29,0:20:51.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vá verificar você mesmo.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:51.40,0:20:53.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Iron Body.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:07.00,0:21:08.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{His giant hammer was...! - OG}O martelo gigante dele...!{PJ}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:08.80,0:21:10.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I-Impossível!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:11.54,0:21:12.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seu filho da...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:13.36,0:21:15.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me larga, desgraçado!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:15.22,0:21:17.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is that Herculean strength\Nof yours your pride? - OG}Você se orgulha dessa\Nsua força descomunal?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:17.88,0:21:22.34,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't move my arm! There's no way my power can be beat... - OG}Não consigo mexer meu braço! Não tem como\Neu perder num duelo de força!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:39.55,0:21:43.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Três dos capatazes foram...!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:49.22,0:21:51.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Get some reinforcements from downstairs! - OG}Chamem reforços lá de baixo!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:51.00,0:21:51.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Shave!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:57.75,0:21:58.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Encontramos eles!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:58.72,0:22:00.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É o Roronoa Zoro!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:00.13,0:22:01.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They finally showed up at last! - OG}Eles finalmente apareceram!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:01.96,0:22:03.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não os deixem escapar!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:03.69,0:22:05.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I saw that woman this afternoon too! - OG}Eu vi essa mulher hoje de tarde também!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:05.05,0:22:06.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Atrás deles!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:06.37,0:22:08.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Cadê o Luffy?!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:08.92,0:22:11.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How should I know?! I wanna ask that question! - OG}Como vou saber?! Eu é que queria saber!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:12.97,0:22:14.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que fazemos?!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:14.29,0:22:18.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now that it's come to this,\Nit's like we've been caught in the act anyway. - OG}A essa altura, é como se\Ntivéssemos sido pegos no flagra.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:18.21,0:22:20.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If we go on the offensive,\Nthere's a way to get in. - OG}Mas atacando de frente dá pra entrar!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:22.40,0:22:24.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What?! Hey, Zoro! What're you gonna do?! - OG}Espera, Zoro! O que você vai fazer?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:24.80,0:22:27.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ficar correndo ao redor do prédio\Nnão vai nos levar a lugar nenhum.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:27.85,0:22:31.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We'll openly plunge in from the front and look for Robin. - OG}Vamos invadir pela frente e encontrar a Robin.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:31.58,0:22:32.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?!\N– O quê?!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:32.97,0:22:36.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas eles são carpinteiros!\NNão são nossos inimigos, sabia?!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:36.56,0:22:39.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't worry. I'll use the back of my swords! - OG}Não se preocupe. Vou usar o dorso das espadas!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:40.51,0:22:44.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Saiam do caminho!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:48.97,0:22:51.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But you're inflicting fatal wounds on them! - OG}– Dá pra matar desse jeito!\N– Dá pra matar desse jeito!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:09.86,0:23:13.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well... I'm shocked. - OG}Bom, isso é uma surpresa.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:13.63,0:23:18.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pra ser sincero, nunca pensei\Nque te veria aqui... Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:19.60,0:23:21.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nós já nos conhecemos?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:21.70,0:23:24.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nos conhecemos pela primeira vez ontem à noite.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:24.19,0:23:28.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But I've wanted to see you all this time. - OG}Mas eu queria te conhecer...\Nhá muito, muito tempo.{JT/Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:30.01,0:23:33.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Até coloquei seu cartaz de procurada\Nno meu quarto pra nunca esquecer.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:34.29,0:23:35.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shall I give you my autograph or something? - OG}Quer um autógrafo?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:37.71,0:23:38.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seria...{OG}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:38.90,0:23:40.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,ótimo!{OG}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:42.52,0:23:43.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então queria me matar?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:44.48,0:23:45.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Exatamente.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:45.91,0:23:47.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Antes que você destrua o mundo!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:49.68,0:23:51.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why do you go searching for the poneglyphs?! - OG}Por que você anda procurando os poneglyphs?!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:53.37,0:23:55.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desde os tempos antigos,
Dialogue: 5,0:23:55.29,0:24:00.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{the government has declared globally that it's a serious felony to seek out and decipher the poneglyphs. - OG}{\q2}o governo declarou universalmente que é crime\Nprocurar e decifrar os poneglyphs.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:00.90,0:24:02.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tenho certeza que sabe disso.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:04.57,0:24:07.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você também sabe da existência\Ndos poneglyphs.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:07.64,0:24:10.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Apenas saber da existência não seria crime.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:10.26,0:24:15.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas... a única pessoa no mundo inteiro\Ncapaz de decifrar aqueles textos...
Dialogue: 5,0:24:15.27,0:24:16.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,é você.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:18.10,0:24:22.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É exatamente por isso que o governo colocou\Numa recompensa tão enorme na sua cabeça,
Dialogue: 5,0:24:22.56,0:24:25.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mesmo você tendo apenas oito anos na época.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:25.51,0:24:28.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É porque você é a única no mundo
Dialogue: 5,0:24:28.20,0:24:31.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,capaz de restaurar a arma ancestral!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:34.33,0:24:37.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendo... Você sabe sobre a arma.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:39.56,0:24:44.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{All things considered, I never thought CP9 was\Nan organization that really existed. - OG}Pensando bem... Nunca achei que a CP9\Nrealmente existisse como organização.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:44.84,0:24:46.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If it does, - OG}E se existe,{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:46.21,0:24:50.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{it means that you've already left the Straw Hat Pirates and have been helping the government. - OG}significa que você deixou os Chapéus de Palha\Ne está ajudando o governo.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:50.84,0:24:54.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's bizarre for a woman who's been on the run\Nfor twenty years to act like that, but... - OG}Comportamento estranho para uma mulher\Nforagida há vinte anos, mas...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:54.65,0:24:58.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{well, that is not my concern. - OG}bom, isso não é da minha conta.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:59.04,0:25:02.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If the weapon gets restored\Nthrough deciphering the Poneglyphs, - OG}Se decifrar os poneglyphs\Nlevar ao retorno da arma,{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:02.11,0:25:05.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{whether its owner is righteous or evil, - OG}o resultado será o mesmo{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:05.02,0:25:07.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{the result will be the same. - OG}{no matter how just or evil its owner. - JT}independente se o dono for bom ou mau.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:08.39,0:25:12.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A arma jamais trará\Npaz a este mundo.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:12.66,0:25:15.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The world will go under for sure. - OG}Ela {\i1}vai{\i0} trazer o fim do mundo.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:16.37,0:25:20.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não devemos invocar uma relíquia do passado!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:23.42,0:25:26.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tem razão. Concordo com você.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:26.45,0:25:28.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But it's none of your business. - OG}Mas também não é da sua conta.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:28.59,0:25:31.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que quer que eu faça para pesquisar a história,
Dialogue: 5,0:25:31.80,0:25:35.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{you, a stranger, have no right\Nto say anything to me. - OG}um estranho como você não tem direito de me dar lição.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:37.28,0:25:40.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well... not quite... - OG}Bom... eu tenho esse direito...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:40.31,0:25:43.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{since you and I are\Nin the same boat, in a sense. - OG}porque, de certo modo,\Nvocê e eu estamos no mesmo barco.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:45.19,0:25:46.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I... - OG}Eu possuo...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:47.41,0:25:50.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I have the blueprints\Nof the ancient weapon Pluton. - OG}as plantas da\Narma ancestral Pluton.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:51.57,0:25:53.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The blueprints of the weapon?! - OG}As plantas da arma?!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:53.64,0:25:58.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pluton é o nome de um navio de guerra\Nconstruído nesta ilha há muito tempo.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:00.41,0:26:05.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The shipbuilding engineer who created\Nthis overwhelmingly powerful weapon... - OG}O antigo engenheiro que criou\Numa arma tão poderosa sentiu que{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:05.31,0:26:11.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He felt that if by some chance Pluton started running out of control, a counterforce would be needed to stop it. - OG}{\q2}se por acaso Pluton saísse do controle,\Numa contramedida seria necessária para pará-la.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:11.33,0:26:15.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então ele passou as plantas\Npara as futuras gerações.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:15.04,0:26:16.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In order to get them... - OG}O governo...{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:16.56,0:26:20.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,finalmente recorreu à força\Npara conseguir essas plantas.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:22.29,0:26:25.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{To think that you're helping them\Nwithout knowing that... - OG}Imagina ajudá-los\Nsem saber de nada disso...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:25.81,0:26:27.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estou chocado demais pra falar.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:28.36,0:26:31.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O homem chamado Tom,\Nque me confiou as plantas,{OG}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:31.45,0:26:37.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{was concerned about a girl who alone was able to escape\Nfrom the Ohara incident twenty years ago. - OG}{\q2}estava preocupado com uma garota que foi a única sobrevivente\Ndo incidente de Ohara há vinte anos.{Z/JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:37.56,0:26:39.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele disse que, embora fosse pequena,
Dialogue: 5,0:26:39.61,0:26:43.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{she was dangerous since she had\Nthe same ideology as those Devils of Ohara. - OG}era perigosa pois compartilhava\Na ideologia dos demônios de Ohara.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:43.37,0:26:48.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I inherited the creator's will,\Nso I have the responsibility of stopping you! - OG}Herdei a vontade do criador,\Ne tenho a responsabilidade de te parar!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:48.51,0:26:51.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now that the government has come\Nto know of the existence of the blueprints, - OG}Agora que o governo sabe\Nque as plantas existem,{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:52.18,0:26:55.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{essentially, it'd be better if I burned them. - OG}seria melhor simplesmente queimá-las.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:55.36,0:27:00.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But I can't do that because you're alive, and so there's still a possibility that the weapon can be restored! - OG}Mas enquanto você estiver viva, não posso fazer isso,\Npois a arma ainda pode ser restaurada!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:27:14.50,0:27:17.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É tudo o que tem a dizer antes de morrer?
Dialogue: 5,0:27:18.57,0:27:24.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Com todo respeito, mesmo que me matasse\Ne impedisse a restauração,
Dialogue: 5,0:27:24.20,0:27:28.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{if the blueprints get stolen from you,\Nwouldn't it be the same thing? - OG}deixar as plantas serem roubadas\Nnão daria no mesmo?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:27:34.26,0:27:35.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom...
Dialogue: 5,0:27:36.53,0:27:39.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,deixe-me dizer mais uma coisa.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:41.78,0:27:44.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're the ones who got taken in by a plan. - OG}Vocês é que caíram no {\i1}meu{\i0} plano.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:27:55.85,0:27:57.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, é isso!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:05.91,0:28:09.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I was finally able to get out! That was terrible. - OG}Finalmente saí! Que terrível.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:28:09.05,0:28:11.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Okay, I'll swoop in this time for sure. - OG}Certo, dessa vez eu entro com tudo.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:28:11.58,0:28:13.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll go capture Robin! - OG}Hora de ir capturar a Robin!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:28:13.73,0:28:17.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 5,0:28:17.27,0:28:21.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Rocket!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:37.59,0:28:40.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're no match for our martial arts skills. - OG}Vocês não são páreo para nossas artes marciais.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:28:43.70,0:28:46.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora, entregue logo...
Dialogue: 5,0:28:47.43,0:28:49.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{or else it'll get dirty with your blood. - OG}ou vai ficar manchado com seu sangue.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:28:52.15,0:28:53.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga...
Dialogue: 5,0:28:54.63,0:28:57.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Achei... que conseguiria derrotá-los.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:07.50,0:29:09.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pra falar a verdade...
Dialogue: 5,0:29:10.07,0:29:14.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Iceburg-[/i1]san[/i0]told me to just run away. - OG}O Iceburg me disse pra simplesmente fugir.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:29:15.02,0:29:20.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele disse pra largar tudo e correr...
Dialogue: 5,0:29:24.17,0:29:25.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,já que...
Dialogue: 5,0:29:26.70,0:29:29.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,é uma falsificação completa!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:30.30,0:29:31.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:31.97,0:29:33.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Falsificação, disse?
Dialogue: 5,0:29:33.45,0:29:35.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que estupidez...
Dialogue: 5,0:29:36.72,0:29:41.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não sei quem vocês são,\Nmas isso significa que o plano de vocês falhou, não é?
Dialogue: 5,0:29:41.14,0:29:44.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que patético. Sinto muito, amigão.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:44.50,0:29:50.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nem sei o que vocês estão procurando.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:50.85,0:29:56.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que atrevimento... Acha que\Nenganou a CP9?
Dialogue: 5,0:29:58.11,0:30:00.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In any case, even though you're only a decoy, - OG}De qualquer forma, pode ser apenas uma isca,{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:30:00.07,0:30:03.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{we can't keep you alive now that you're involved. - OG}mas não podemos te deixar viver\Nagora que está envolvido.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:30:17.95,0:30:22.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I got stuck! Dammit! I got stuck again! - OG}Estou preso! Droga! Fiquei preso de novo!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:30:22.55,0:30:24.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que isso sempre acontece?!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:24.18,0:30:25.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha...!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:25.47,0:30:26.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 5,0:30:26.71,0:30:28.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah! O cara da corda!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:28.55,0:30:31.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu com você? Tá bem?
Dialogue: 5,0:30:31.51,0:30:35.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tá coberto de sangue.\NVocê é cheio de surpresas!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:35.04,0:30:38.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That'd be you! This is the third floor! - OG}Eu é que digo! Isso aqui é o terceiro andar!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:30:39.48,0:30:41.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha Luffy...
Dialogue: 5,0:30:41.15,0:30:44.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So you took the trouble to come\Nto take the crime upon yourself? - OG}Veio até aqui pra assumir a culpa?
Dialogue: 5,0:30:45.44,0:30:46.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah! Máscaras!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:46.62,0:30:48.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are they masks?! - OG}Vocês estão de máscara?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:30:48.15,0:30:52.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then you people must be the ones\Nwho're making Robin do stuff! Give Robin back to us, you damn bastards! - OG}Então vocês são os desgraçados que estão usando a Robin!\NDevolvam a Robin, seus malditos!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:30:54.23,0:30:57.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga! Ei! Falem alguma coisa!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:57.05,0:30:58.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Tempest Kick.
Dialogue: 5,0:31:06.45,0:31:07.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:12.36,0:31:13.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{His kick cut the wall! - OG}O chute dele cortou a parede!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:31:16.02,0:31:17.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:29.44,0:31:31.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que diabos são esses?
Dialogue: 5,0:31:32.25,0:31:34.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Temos uma emergência.
Dialogue: 5,0:31:34.35,0:31:36.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não temos tempo pra você.
Dialogue: 5,0:31:36.33,0:31:37.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não consigo me mexer!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:37.55,0:31:40.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, imobilizem esse cara também.\NNão temos tempo pra lutar.
Dialogue: 5,0:31:40.65,0:31:41.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo...
Dialogue: 5,0:31:57.87,0:32:01.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's me. A problem occurred in our plan. - OG}Sou eu. Nosso plano teve um imprevisto.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:32:01.35,0:32:03.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Everyone, come to the bedroomright away. - OG}Todos, venham ao quarto imediatamente.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:32:03.75,0:32:05.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Não atirem no Iceburg ainda.
Dialogue: 5,0:32:06.44,0:32:10.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Entenderam? {\i0}Não{\i1} atirem no Iceburg ainda.
Dialogue: 5,0:32:13.95,0:32:16.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wouldn't have minded playing\Nwith you a little longer, but... - OG}Queria ter mais tempo\Npra brincar com vocês, porém...{JT/Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:32:17.73,0:32:20.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but something came up. So, excuse me. - OG}Perdão, mas surgiu algo.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:32:20.14,0:32:21.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Está tentando fugir?!
Dialogue: 5,0:32:22.08,0:32:23.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não.
Dialogue: 5,0:32:30.20,0:32:32.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Since something came up,\NI gave him a finishing blow. - OG}Preciso ir pra outro lugar,\Nentão aqui vai meu golpe final.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:32:32.70,0:32:34.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ahhh! Lulu-san is...! - OG}Ah! Lulu caiu!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:32:34.39,0:32:36.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{By just one hit?! - OG}Com um golpe só?!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:32:35.13,0:32:36.02,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 5,0:32:39.39,0:32:40.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He flew again! - OG}{There she goes again! - JT}Ela está voando de novo!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:32:42.33,0:32:44.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você está... bem?
Dialogue: 5,0:32:46.76,0:32:49.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso não é nada!
Dialogue: 5,0:32:49.40,0:32:54.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendo. Chapéu de Palha, o que veio fazer aqui?
Dialogue: 5,0:32:54.90,0:32:57.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todo mundo acha que vocês são os culpados.{OG}
Dialogue: 5,0:32:57.75,0:33:01.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry... It was all\Nbecause of our wrong assumption. - OG}Desculpe... Isso tudo foi porque\Nassumimos erroneamente sua culpa.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:33:01.71,0:33:05.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe com isso.\NEstamos acostumados a ser perseguidos.
Dialogue: 5,0:33:05.73,0:33:09.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mais importante, uma membro\Nda nossa tripulação foi levada por mascarados.
Dialogue: 5,0:33:09.96,0:33:11.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então vim buscá-la de volta.
Dialogue: 5,0:33:13.34,0:33:15.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're talking about Nico Robin, right? - OG}Nico Robin, certo?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:33:19.86,0:33:22.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're strong when you fight, right? - OG}Você parece ser um lutador forte.
Dialogue: 5,0:33:22.23,0:33:23.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, sou sim!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:24.42,0:33:25.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Consegue vencê-los?
Dialogue: 5,0:33:26.30,0:33:27.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim, consigo!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:29.82,0:33:33.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então lute comigo! Eu também quero acabar com eles!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:33.10,0:33:33.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você quer...
Dialogue: 5,0:33:33.70,0:33:34.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Claro que quero!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:34.91,0:33:40.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why... Why does Iceburg-san have to be killed by some totally strange idiots?! - OG}Por que... Por que o Iceburg tem que morrer\Nnas mãos de uns idiotas malucos?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:33:40.66,0:33:43.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me poupe!\NQuem diabos são essas pessoas?!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:43.85,0:33:46.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pro inferno com esses agentes secretos malditos!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:48.88,0:33:53.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He was... my teacher. - OG}Aquele homem... É meu mestre.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:33:53.89,0:33:56.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele me ajudou a me tornar um mestre carpinteiro!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:56.31,0:33:58.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why would someone like him be... - OG}Por que fazer isso com alguém assim?!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:33:58.14,0:34:00.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But you're too injured to... - OG}Mas você não está em condição de...{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:34:00.24,0:34:03.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu disse que quero bater\Nnesses idiotas até não poder mais!
Dialogue: 5,0:34:03.49,0:34:06.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem liga pro que acontece\Ncom meu corpo depois disso?!
Dialogue: 5,0:34:09.14,0:34:11.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna fight to\Nthe very last bone in my body! - OG}Vou lutar até sobrar só osso!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:34:11.95,0:34:14.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga! Tirem isso!
Dialogue: 5,0:34:14.85,0:34:18.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo! Tirem isso! Droga!
Dialogue: 5,0:34:42.44,0:34:43.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vão pra casa!
Dialogue: 5,0:34:45.35,0:34:47.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've got nothing I could give you people! - OG}Não tenho nada pra dar a vocês!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:34:48.11,0:34:49.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso nos coloca numa situação difícil.
Dialogue: 5,0:34:57.08,0:35:00.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What should I tell you first... - OG}Por onde devo começar...{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:35:03.13,0:35:04.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{when you're about to die? - OG}agora que está prestes a morrer?{JT/Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:35:05.54,0:35:08.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You disappointed me. - OG}Você me decepcionou.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:35:12.60,0:35:14.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lucci!
Dialogue: 5,0:35:14.30,0:35:16.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A culpa é sua.
Dialogue: 5,0:35:19.39,0:35:23.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You should've given them to the government\Nwhen they asked nicely. - OG}Devia ter entregado ao governo\Nquando pediram educadamente.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:35:24.44,0:35:26.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kaku!
Dialogue: 5,0:35:26.59,0:35:32.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If possible, I wanted to make this town\Npart of my memory without hurting you. - OG}Queria que minhas memórias desta cidade\Nnão incluíssem machucar você.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:35:33.39,0:35:35.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kalifa...
Dialogue: 5,0:35:35.15,0:35:38.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então você também herdou a\Nteimosia do seu mestre, né?
Dialogue: 5,0:35:38.05,0:35:40.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Blueno, do bar...
Dialogue: 5,0:35:41.01,0:35:46.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês... trabalham... pro governo?
Dialogue: 5,0:35:46.37,0:35:47.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Exato.
Dialogue: 5,0:35:47.42,0:35:51.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Trabalhar disfarçados foi uma missão bem fácil pra nós.
Dialogue: 5,0:35:52.56,0:35:57.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In any case, your prudence leaves me\Nat a loss for words. - OG}Devo dizer, sua astúcia\Nme deixa sem palavras.{Z/JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:35:59.23,0:36:01.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, Iceburg-[/i1]san[/i0]... - OG}Agora, Iceburg...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:36:02.07,0:36:06.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde estão as plantas\Nda arma ancestral Pluton?
Dialogue: 5,0:36:07.00,0:36:11.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Please tell us, before many people get hurt. - OG}A menos que queira que mais gente se machuque,\Npor favor nos diga o que queremos saber.{Z}
